# Project Context

Monorepo containing 4 UK niche accountancy websites. All live, deployed on Vercel (auto-deploys from `main` branch), sharing a common architecture. Last updated: 3 April 2026.

## Sites

| Site | Domain | niche_id | Blog URL pattern | Posts |
|------|--------|----------|-----------------|-------|
| Property Tax Partners | propertytaxpartners.co.uk | property | /blog/{category}/{slug} | 85 |
| Dental Finance Partners | dentalfinancepartners.co.uk | dentists | /blog/{category}/{slug} | 55 |
| Medical Accountants UK | medicalaccountantsuk.co.uk | medical | /blog/{slug} (flat) | 46 |
| Accounts for Lawyers | accountsforlawyers.co.uk | solicitors | /blog/{category}/{slug} | 50 |

Medical uses flat blog URLs (no category in path). The other 3 use /blog/{category-slug}/{post-slug}.

## Tech Stack

- Next.js 15 + React 19 + TypeScript + Tailwind 4
- App Router (src/app/)
- Supabase (leads, blog topics)
- Vercel deployment (auto-deploys from main branch on git push)
- Python (Anthropic API) for blog content generation
- GSC/GA4 integration via agents/

